  </data>
    <data name="Step2_Desc" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>In 'Settings', define your secret XOR key. Use the 'Extensions to encrypt' section to add specific formats (e.g., .txt, .docx). Only files with these extensions will be encrypted during the backup process.</value>
  </data>
